case.title: Tryna go out tonight!! - 26 (bx, the city)
case.text:
Hey its Sat night an i'm just bored chillin an i just wanna go out, summer ain't gone be here forever lol
I'm 26 years old, single, i'm 6'1, good shape an i'm just looking for a cute, fun, attractive woman to go out with. I'm in the bx but we can go to the city to a bar, lounge or whatever we come up with
I'm very real, you be too, an please no flakes, i just wanna go out an have a good night :)
Btw please put " tonight" as your email subj so i can get rid of the spam
